	(2693, 'disgust', 'A gathering of a social sports club at which they proceeded to á\nshow pornographic videos and then afterwards (when most people á\nhad had quite a bit to drink) carried on in a very degrading, á\nunmoral manner - especially females exposing and flaunting á\nthemselves with no shame or embarassment.'),
	(2694, 'shame', 'Like guilt - the most ashamed I have ever felt was when I began á\nto feel guilty about having sex with my boyfriend when it was á\nonly "the thing to do", and not really an act of love.'),
