	(2697, 'anger', 'Because I am the Captain of a basketball team I usually organise á\na roster system so that everyone in the team can have a turn at á\ndoing either a duty or a ref. A lot of the time the girls can\'t á\nbe bothered or just forget - I usually have to fill in.'),
