	(2709, 'sadness', 'This occurred when my girlfriend and I have to finish our á\nrelationship due to some circumstances between her and her á\nfamily. I was really sad, hurt and couldn\'t really find any á\nreason why am I still living. Is this life is all about ? This á\nwas one of few question which crept up vividly every time I á\nthought about what had happened.'),
	(2710, 'disgust', 'I\'m very disgusted when I see people abusing their body with á\ndrugs and alcohol. They take advantage of these things usually á\nfor an excuse for the fantasies which they like and so they do á\nthings stupidly and unjustly.'),
