	(2730, 'fear', 'My daughter was 2 yrs she went up to a colt tried to hit it. It á\nturned on her and kicked her over the heart, sent her flying á\nthrough the air. I left my mother and sister to deal to her as á\nthey are nurses. I felt I didn\'t want to know if she was going to á\ndie, it was just too much.'),
