	(4368, 'shame', 'A friend of mine had said something about not liking to come to á\nmy place just before coming to my place.   In the meanwhile I got á\nto learn about this from another friend of mine and when she á\narrived at my place I really treated her badly.  I was later á\nashamed of the way I had treated someone when the person was at á\nmy place.'),
