	(4390, 'sadness', 'Once my friend and I got into into a hot discussion on a very á\ncontroversial topic.  At one point of the argument I disagreed á\nwith her totally and I took what she was saying as an insult.  So á\nI couter-argued and unknowingly hurt her emotionally, I felt very á\nsad about this.'),
